Layer.Name: ntt_epsg_3034
Layer.Title: Gridded estimates of travel times for nitrate in the unsaturated zone in six european countries
Layer.Abstract: This dataset consists of gridded estimates of travel times for nitrate in the unsaturated zone for Great Britain (UK), France, the Netherlands, Denmark, Croatia and Slovenia. Data for Croatia and Slovenia are presented from a regional scale pilot study, with data from the remaining countries at the national scale. The dataset was developed in Work Package 5 of the GeoERA Groundwater project HOVER.
